Skills.Description: Grants ongoing HP recovery on all allies by <color=red>{0}%</color> of ATK for 15s. Also cancels 3x Debuff effects if Red Elemental. Further grants <code=200,param=1000><color=#3398f1>Demon Power</color> for 10s if Attacker.
